Testing for this issue is manual. Run an instance and check that it (generally) shows up in:

{code}
/var/run/eucalyptus/global_network_info.xml
{code}

on the cloud controller within a second and always under the minimum interval between broadcasts (5 seconds) + some allowance for the run call to the cluster controller.

This is easier to verify in vpc mode as there was more delay prior to the fix.
